  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b95\u0bc6\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No Private Bus Services in Protest Areas - Kemunu",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kemunuwijayaratna has said that private bus services will not operate near the areas where protests will take place tomorrow (09).",
        "He said that it has been decided not to engage in transport services near the areas where the protests are taking place as the use of detours will cost more fuel if the police close the streets.",
        "He said that we will not be able to engage in bus services tomorrow but we are not against people's protest."
      ],
